text: Giuseppe Lupi (born 17 November 1894, date of death unknown) was an Italian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Italian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Genoa
